\f4\b\fs29\fsmilli14667 \cf0 Bowl with floral and abstract motifs and inscription\uc0\u8232 
\f1\b0 Joseon dynasty (1392\'961910), dated 1847\uc0\u8232 Porcelain with underglaze cobalt-blue design
