\f4\b\fs29\fsmilli14667 \cf0 Cup with handle\uc0\u8232 
\f1\b0 Goryeo dynasty (918\'961392), 13th century\uc0\u8232 Stoneware with inlaid and molded design under celadon glaze
\f0\fs24 \
\pard\pardeftab720\sa320\partightenfactor0

